In this section its just about file structure you should work on any projects there is proper ways to do your file structure
mostly it helps you to keep track of your project most of project follow the mvc(Model, View, Controller) pattern.

here is some examples of it
--Lets consider the project of the shopping cart
  file structure as follow

  ---Controller
      -auth.js 
      -product.js 
      -order.js 
 ---Model
     -product.js 
     -order.js
     -user.js
 ---routes
     -app.js

The structure make things easier.
